content.rendered:
To start of the year, Tesla Club Indonesia decided to hold an event at the shooting range! Here members had a chance to test their aim as well as had a chance to discuss Tesla matters. / Mengawali tahun baru, Tesla Club Indonesia mengadakan acara di lapangan tembak! Selain menjalin silaturahmi dengan sesama pemilik Tesla, para anggota yang hadir juga memiliki kesempatan untuk membahas masalah Tesla.
